title: March Mortourum
author: fadedsoul
pages:
#-          MARCH
      MORTOURUM 


          THE
         BOOK
           OF
     SPERIANITY   
#-     MARISORIUM I

   "THE BEGINNING"
#- When the universe began, the Gods and Goddesses had just created the world.

They then saw that the creatures of the world where too cold, so they created the sun. But then they where dieing of thirst, so they created water.
#- The creatures also needed challenge, so they created night time where it was dark.

But Morsius, the God of Death, thought this was too little. Against the other God's wills, and created monsters that are pulled into the world from his soul at night.
#- For this, the other Gods cast him into a new realm they created, that we call the Nether. The Nether, also referable to as Hell, is a terrible place full of lava and red rock.

There are evil rituals that can be performed to make portals to 
#- this realm. But when they cast him there, he made a dragon, that made energy that destroyed anything it touched. They cast this dragon into a small pearl, but do to the energy called Ender Energy, they duplicated. They where spread around the world.
#-  Then after the deal with the God of Death, Termusio, the God of Musis and Language, gave his gifts to the creatures of the world.
#-      MARISORIUM II

  "THE WAR OF GODS"
#- Mylar, the God of Space, thought Morsius should have more punishment, while others thought he had had enough punishment. So the Gods split into factions. The factions battled and battled until most gods where dead. Only 6 remained.
They are the following:
#- Morsius,the God of Death; Termusio, the God of Music and Language; Sorsiomius, the God of Dance and the Magic; Lorkias, the God of Life; Hercoulesius, the God of The Craft; And Munlicharious, the leader of the Gods, and handled everything left over.
#-      PARSIUSIUMOSO 
             I


 "BEGINNING OF A 
       SPECIES"
#- The Gods managed things, but did not have emotions nor could move so no more wars broke out.

So the creatures took control.

The ones that got the Gifts of Language and Music where Humans.
#- They started forming civilisations and making clans.   This era would be known as Civcraft I. 
The Humans could not be like the now vegetable like gods, as the Humans where now violent and made terrible wars.


#- So the humans started making books, art, and magnificent structures.

The other creatures did not fail though, they dominated the jungles and mountains.

But the Humans where much more important.
#- They started sailing oceans, and making watercrafts.

They eventually became even more powerful than the Gods. So they made war on the Gods, trying to destroy them.
#- They went up to the sky realm of Hyroriusium, and slayed the Gods.

But when they took the energies, they could not handle it. So they found portals in Hyroriusium that when the energy cast into them and mixed with the Ender Energy, it sent 
#- duplicates of the portals around the world to the mysterious realm of the End. Humans started hunting for them, but finding the pearls made in the beginning. They used them as prisons, sending the people to the End in Era I and Era II.
#-        FADEDSOUL I

 "THE END OF AN ERA"
#- I have found this book and I have translated it. It shall be House Darsk's official religion. 

In other scripts I read things about repeating history.

This may mean that Era II could be coming to a close.
#-  The world could end.

Civilisations would fall, fire flailing from the sky destroying everything.

It will kill us all, but it also may open a new Era. It could have the Gods reborn with the energy released from the End.
#- They could start a New Beginning, a Third Era.


   The Third Era is here, the sky is closing, we must try and survive the Apocolypse. Darsk is based on peace, and an Apocolypse defies that.
#- So we, declare that we shall not face anything like this. We will hide in the End,Hell, and anywhere inbetween. We will not die out. For we are all Humans. We must band together for the Apocolypse these scripts predict.

We must survive.
#- 


         -----
